  description : "JUEX-L2-000050 - The Juniper EX switch must be configured to permit authorized users to select a user session to capture."
  info        : "Without the capability to select a user session to capture/record or view/hear, investigations into suspicious or harmful events would be hampered by the volume of information captured. The volume of information captured may also adversely impact the operation for the network. Session audits may include port mirroring, tracking websites visited, and recording information and/or file transfers.

NOTE: Nessus has provided the target output to assist in reviewing the benchmark to ensure target compliance."
